data.description: Solar Efficient Home in the Preston Lake Community. Imagine living in a neighborhood with a community clubhouse, pool, walking trails, lake, and park. Don't miss out on the opportunity to see this stunning one-level home! The house boasts a large, open floor plan with ample natural light. It also includes a stunning ensuite, dining room, and a remarkable kitchen. You are going to notice the trim work and moldings right away. The property is equipped with solar panels, effectively eliminating any electricity-related costs. The seller takes full responsibility for paying off the panels upon closing. The unfinished basement offers endless possibilities, whether you need additional storage space or want to add finished square footage to your home. The outdoor space includes a screened porch, front porch, and paver patio for relaxation. If you are in search of a comfortable and beautiful house, make sure to check this one out!
